{"tid":1246012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣令年青人以外嘅人知道更多？","createTime":"2019-06-20T13:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T14:13:57.000Z","uid":99207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"25e509bc5f29d14e934941b47079a064f6f54375","tid":1246012,"uid":99207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:58:56.000Z","msg":"其實由612部署至今<br />\n絕大部份嘅策略、部署、資訊、行動細節等，都係出現喺連登，而大家都知道連登入面後生仔佔咗好大嘅比例<br />\n就算612有Telegram group/channel，用嘅人絕人部份又係後生仔<br />\n舉個例，上次塞地鐵單野我屋企人係完全唔知咩事，到夜晚睇新聞先知；612出去野餐，我地有齊戰略組醫療組文宣組物資組支援組，但基本上都係得年輕一代知咩事，屋企人甚至當日朝早都仲以為我地係去和平集會<br />\n發夢見到612嗰日立法會外面嗰啲99%都係後生仔<br />\n我敢講如果將來嘅資訊可以喺不同年齡層廣泛地流通，我地嘅力量一定會更大<br />\n所以我地唔可以再將資訊局限於連登/Telegram<br />\n無論係裝備、物資、策略、組織等，都一定要俾更多人知，否則621大家出嚟見到嘅又會好似上次咁99%後生仔，而大人就繼續咩都唔知咁走去返工<br />\n<br />\n我地一定要將資訊喺其他平台傳出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但要做到匿名同高度安全，真係好難<br />\n全能嘅鍵盤戰士出嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1274139337c93941d45ece293d1dc232fa352773","tid":1246012,"uid":99207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:00:42.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a0241a4e4f7f9400da2b45216fb2db0da8a35b","tid":1246012,"uid":99207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:02:06.000Z","msg":"除咗連仔提供個咁安全嘅討論平台<br />\n同埋sever設於外國嘅Telegram<br />\n仲有咩平台可以令群眾力量變大<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a297466c77f615aa36929af130383a4d00537aa","tid":1246012,"uid":200158,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:02:49.000Z","msg":"聽完trumptrump講，香港人應直插真普選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242618</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"93a62cd9c42536906978694ae9d7876daa72edcf","tid":1246012,"uid":99207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:03:53.000Z","msg":"唔好俾道氣散啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n200萬人入面有好多人仲未知咩事架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc55820373d0633cbb8f0eb26d669aa9ba51f9fc","tid":1246012,"uid":99207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:08:38.000Z","msg":"出嚟啦自由閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ed1997e22ee67ce0bf2b5880272f88792ca818","tid":1246012,"uid":99207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:13:57.000Z","msg":"最後一推算了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}